description: This skill provides facts about the regular cast of characters on the five Star Trek television series that have aired to date. Some facts are fairly well-known; others are bits of interesting trivia that we learn in a single episode. All facts are canon from the televised scripts -- no novels or other material were used. This skill is not authorized by the copyright holders of Star Trek.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask trek characters to tell me a fact
Alexa, ask trek characters to tell me something
Alexa, ask trek characters for a fact
name: Unauthorized Trek Characters
shortDescription: Learn facts about your favorite Star Trek characters. Covers all five television series. Unauthorized.
